msgid "maxframe.tensor.sin"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:1 of
msgid "Trigonometric sine, element-wise."
msgstr "三角正弦，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:3 of
msgid "Angle, in radians (:math:`2 \\pi` rad equals 360 degrees)."
msgstr "角度，以弧度为单位（:math:`2 \\pi` 弧度等于 360 度）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:15 of
msgid "**y** -- The sine of each element of x."
msgstr "**y** -- x 中每个元素的正弦值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`arcsin`, :py:obj:`sinh`, :py:obj:`cos`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sin.sin:22 of
msgid ""
"The sine is one of the fundamental functions of trigonometry (the "
"mathematical study of triangles).  Consider a circle of radius 1 centered"
" on the origin.  A ray comes in from the :math:`+x` axis, makes an angle "
"at the origin (measured counter-clockwise from that axis), and departs "
"from the origin.  The :math:`y` coordinate of the outgoing ray's "
"intersection with the unit circle is the sine of that angle.  It ranges "
"from -1 for :math:`x=3\\pi / 2` to +1 for :math:`\\pi / 2.`  The function"
" has zeroes where the angle is a multiple of :math:`\\pi`. Sines of "
"angles between :math:`\\pi` and :math:`2\\pi` are negative. The numerous "
"properties of the sine and related functions are included in any standard"
" trigonometry text."
msgstr ""
"正弦是三角学（研究三角形的数学）的基本函数之一。考虑一个以原点为中心、"
"半径为 1 的圆。一条射线从 :math:`+x` 轴进入，在原点处形成一个角度（从该轴"
"逆时针测量），然后从原点出发。出射射线与单位圆交点的 :math:`y` 坐标即为该"
"角度的正弦值。当 :math:`x=3\\pi / 2` 时为 -1，当 :math:`\\pi / 2` 时为 +1"
"。当角度为 :math:`\\pi` 的倍数时，函数值为零。在 :math:`\\pi` 和 :math:`2"
"\\pi` 之间的角度，其正弦值为负。正弦及相关函数的众多性质在任何标准三角学"
"教材中都有介绍。"

